@node Glissando
@unnumberedsubsubsec Glissando

@cindex glissando
@funindex \glissando
@funindex glissando

A @notation{glissando} is created by attaching @code{\glissando}
to a note:

@lilypond[verbatim,quote,relative=2]
g2\glissando g'
c2\glissando c,
@end lilypond

Different styles of glissandi can be created.  For details, see
@ref{Line styles}.

